1
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,980
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:39,480
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

3
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:45,260
♪Rereading it now,
I think it's just a joke in life♪

4
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:49,580
♪During my beautiful youth,
I longed for peace♪

5
00:00:49,740 --> 00:00:53,240
♪I vowed to face challenges with you
before Buddha♪

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:59,380
♪I pray to the gods not to be alone♪

7
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,140
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

8
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:06,300
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

9
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Even though the streets are bustling,
I can only watch alone♪

10
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Spend years on the sea,
drifting through foreign lands♪

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:20,580
♪There have been
reunions and separations♪

12
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:26,300
♪There are countless sceneries,
none of them are half as good as you♪

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,180
♪I asked heaven and earth
where we can share the bright moon♪

14
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:33,340
♪Looking back,
only the wind understands♪

15
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪Turns out that when love is deep,
right and wrong are forgotten♪

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,500
♪Let me ask you
how black hair turns white?♪

17
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:47,180
♪I answer myself,
saying it's been a long separation♪

18
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:53,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:04,680
=Cao Xuanxuan's Love Journey=

20
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,220
=Episode 4=

21
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:11,960
Father,

22
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,360
I heard you wanted to see me.

23
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,480
Zilu,

24
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:26,080
I heard Imperial Envoy likes
calligraphy and paintings.

25
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,680
Go to the study and pick a few nice ones

26
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,640
to send to the Imperial Envoy.

27
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:32,640
Father,

28
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,000
you were

29
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,600
never fond of dealing with officials.

30
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,960
Why would you want me

31
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,120
to send something now?

32
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,220
Master is worried
about Young Master Zijie.

33
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,960
Father,

34
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,600
in my opinion,

35
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,240
Zijie has his own fate.

36
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,720
If he's really foolish,

37
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,460
nothing you give
to the official will help.

38
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:50,800
Stop wasting time

39
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,040
and do what I say.

40
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,240
All right.

41
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,240
Calm down.

42
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,160
I will go

43
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,760
and get it done now.

44
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,880
Young Master Zilu,

45
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,760
this case

46
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,920
has not been solved yet.

47
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,600
Keep an eye on it.

48
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,640
Make sure he doesn't solve this case.

49
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,320
Rest assured.

50
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:14,920
He won't.

51
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,040
Everyone, please look at this.

52
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,560
Isn't this

53
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,640
an ordinary house?

54
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:31,060
What's so special about it?

55
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:35,720
It's...

56
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:36,720
It's...

57
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,980
Why does it look like this?

58
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,080
Sir,

59
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,680
people say

60
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,280
seeing is believing.

61
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,320
But sometimes, what we see

62
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,280
isn't the truth.

63
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,880
In certain situations,

64
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,760
we can experience optical illusions.

65
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,960
Optical illusions?

66
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,960
What does that mean?

67
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,420
I've never heard of it before.

68
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,160
Zhao Qiang,

69
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,400
you killed Fu Miao

70
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,360
and staged this entire scene.

71
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,960
I've never heard

72
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,320
of optical illusions.

73
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,880
You still won't budge, huh?

74
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:03,560
Fine.

75
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,640
I'll make you admit it.

76
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,920
Sorry

77
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,180
for stealing your spotlight.

78
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:16,640
Well,

79
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,480
sir.

80
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,200
My child bride here

81
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,480
loves solving cases.

82
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,800
She overheard me

83
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,040
when I was deducing the case.

84
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,560
Zhao Qiang,

85
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,480
these pieces of board were found

86
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,600
by my men near the inn in the woods.

87
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,400
You stayed in that storage room
that night.

88
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,280
Are you going to say

89
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,160
you didn't notice

90
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,280
the house

91
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,720
was just some wooden board?

92
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:49,760
I...

93
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,160
Summon

94
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,760
the witness, Zhang Qin.

95
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,400
Greetings, sir.

96
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,040
You, animal.

97
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,800
Don't do it.

98
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,020
Xiaohua, don't be scared.

99
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,600
What's the matter?

100
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,080
Are you scared now?

101
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,000
But that's not the only crime
you've committed.

102
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,240
You violated Zhang Qin,

103
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,780
and her daughter, Xiaohua, saw you.

104
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:57,880
You then planned to kill her
to cover up your crime.

105
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,960
You used the Fox Spirit as a scapegoat

106
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,200
to kill Xiaohua.

107
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,560
When that didn't work,

108
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,760
you framed your classmate, Li Ye.

109
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,640
You've taken two lives,

110
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,520
and you deserve to be executed!

111
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,120
Sir,

112
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,200
I'm innocent.

113
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,120
I didn't do it.

114
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:19,680
It was her.

115
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,800
It was this widow

116
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,040
who failed to seduce me.

117
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,280
So she's trying to frame me.

118
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,040
Nonsense!

119
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:24,960
Sir,

120
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,640
please seek justice for me.

121
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,120
Didn't you send

122
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,280
He Chun to follow me?

123
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,360
How could I possibly

124
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,520
harm Xiaohua

125
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,740
under her surveillance?

126
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,840
It's precisely you knew

127
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:34,960
He Chun was following you

128
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:37,120
so you exposed
your whereabouts to her

129
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,160
to clear yourself of suspicion.

130
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,760
That day,

131
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:44,440
He Chun saw you bought
four skewers of candied hawthorn

132
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,800
and gave them to four children.

133
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,920
But Xiaohua wasn't among them.

134
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,200
You

135
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,520
only had to take one candied hawthorn

136
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,600
off from every skewer

137
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,520
and stick them to a new skewer,

138
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,720
to make five skewers.

139
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,600
Then you used the candied hawthorn

140
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:58,800
to lure Xiaohua

141
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,080
into the trap

142
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,640
you had set on the mountain.

143
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,540
As for the evidence,

144
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:07,360
the old man selling
the candied hawthorn noticed

145
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,240
that he was one skewer short

146
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,880
after you left.

147
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,240
Sir,

148
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,240
it was only a skewer.

149
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,560
It cannot prove

150
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,960
that I took it.

151
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,200
Zhao Qiang,

152
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,160
I thought you had potential.

153
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,020
But you're nothing but a disappointment.

154
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,520
Open your eyes
and look who is behind you!

155
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,960
Xiaohua.

156
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,200
Xiaohua, don't be scared.

157
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,360
Tell me

158
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,720
if the one

159
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,560
who hurt you is here.

160
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,560
Don't be scared.

161
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,680
Don't be scared.

162
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,120
It's him.

163
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,080
Xiaohua.

164
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:54,720
Look

165
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,000
what I have.

166
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,080
It's candied hawthorn.

167
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,380
Do you want it?

168
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:01,860
You can have it.

169
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:03,440
Is it tasty?

170
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,700
Do you want to eat something else?

171
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:07,020
There are still plenty over there.

172
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,380
How about I take you to have some?

173
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:09,440
Let's go.

174
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,160
What a ruthless scholar.

175
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,360
Speak the truth now

176
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,160
or else

177
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,200
don't blame me

178
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,760
for using harsh punishment!

179
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,520
The truth is clear now.

180
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:36,800
I hereby sentence

181
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,360
the criminal, Zhao Qiang,

182
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,020
to be executed immediately!

183
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:41,540
(Order)

184
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,680
Why?

185
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,520
Why?

186
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,440
Aren't you and my husband close friends?

187
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:58,200
Why did you kill him?

188
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,680
That's right.

189
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,560
I killed Fu Miao.

190
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,800
He was just a poor scholar.

191
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:10,200
I promised I'd help him pass
the Provincial Examination.

192
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,000
But he reported me for cheating!

193
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,440
He deserved to die.

194
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,440
And you!

195
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,920
I never wanted to kill you.

196
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,480
But she saw

197
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,600
what I did to her mother.

198
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,240
I had no choice but to kill her.

199
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,200
You, animal.

200
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,240
You two.

201
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,960
I planned everything

202
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,360
so perfectly.

203
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,880
But you two saw through it

204
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,720
so easily.

205
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,240
Why?

206
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,680
I can't accept this!

207
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:43,960
Take him away!

208
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,000
Yes, sir.

209
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:45,480
Move!

210
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,080
Get up!

211
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,240
Magistrate Guo,

212
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,760
you've changed my view of you.

213
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,240
Thank you, sir.

214
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,640
Master!

215
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:05,640
Master,

216
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,640
the case is solved.

217
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:07,480
The killer

218
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,480
is Zhao Qiang.

219
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,280
Really?

220
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:10,360
There's no mistake.

221
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,360
That Zhao Qiang

222
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:12,840
is going to the execution ground.

223
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,520
That's great.

224
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,520
That's great.

225
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:17,160
Young Master Zijie has made something.

226
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:17,840
Master.

227
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,120
This time,

228
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,800
you can rest assured now, right?

229
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,040
He did well.

230
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,720
This case was solved

231
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:30,680
thanks to everyone.

232
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,240
Here.

233
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,640
A toast to all of you.

234
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,880
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

235
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,760
Everyone, have a seat.

236
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,400
Eat up.

237
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,280
He Chun,

238
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,080
I always thought

239
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,880
you were only good at martial arts.

240
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,200
But

241
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,380
you really live up
to Mr. He's reputation.

242
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:52,800
You have

243
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,440
my respect.

244
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,520
Thank you, sir.

245
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:02,680
As for you, Xuanxuan.

246
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,080
I admit

247
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,000
that I never noticed this before.

248
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,600
But now I noticed

249
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,760
you seemed

250
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,880
to be pretty clever.

251
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,000
I'm very capable.

252
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:12,480
Here.

253
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,640
A toast to you too.

254
00:11:22,980 --> 00:11:24,160
Please, enjoy your meal.

255
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:25,320
You should enjoy it too.

256
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,600
Magistrate Guo,

257
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:28,560
what about me?

258
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:32,920
Well...

259
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,760
You...

260
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,200
You look in good spirits today.

261
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,600
Good spirits?

262
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,000
Well,

263
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,560
you are smart.

264
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,520
But you're a little sharp-tongued.

265
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,600
She's right.

266
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:55,920
Tell me.

267
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,960
Have you ever worked

268
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,940
on similar cases

269
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,960
like optical illusions

270
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,340
or a secret chamber murder?

271
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,440
We have never

272
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,520
had such cases before

273
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,440
Listen. The case

274
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,440
is already solved.

275
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,800
We're here to drink today.

276
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:13,800
So stop talking

277
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,520
about those weird

278
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:15,840
and incomprehensible things.

279
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,280
All right. Let's drink.

280
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,480
Waiter!

281
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,560
Serve the wine.

282
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,160
Coming right up!

283
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,120
Sir,

284
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:22,880
here's your wine.

285
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:23,480
All right.

286
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,440
Today,

287
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,480
we will drink

288
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,160
until we drop!

289
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:26,880
All right.

290
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,240
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

291
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,180
Drink until we drop!

292
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:33,860
(Guo Residence)

293
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,020
Young Master Zilu,

